Titolo: Jade Dynasty (video game)

Anno: 2007

Descrizione: Jade Dynasty (also known as Zhu Xian (Chinese: 诛仙)) was a free-to-play MMORPG game created by Perfect World.
Jade Dynasty recently released its seventh major expansion, Jade Dynasty: Dance of the Gevrin, increasing the number of factions to 17. It is based on a popular Chinese internet novel Zhu Xian. On May 1, 2018, it was announced that all game servers would be shut down on June 5, 2018. Ever since the shutdown of 'Official', there have been many appearances of private servers trying to recreate what was once quite a popular Chinese MMORPG.